{"type":"message","id":"966f7928","parentId":"3c525d14","timestamp":"2026-04-22T02:10:26.416Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_cd7f2733ddedc69e93a27e89cbf41c28\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51b6afc714b8c4a17df78a2eac9\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cd7f2733ddedc69e93a27e89cbf41c28\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_cd7f2733ddedc69e93a27e89cbf41c28\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-22 10:10 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_cd7f2733ddedc69e93a27e89cbf41c28\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_cd7f2733ddedc69e93a27e89cbf41c28\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_cd7f2733ddedc69e93a27e89cbf41c28\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51b6afc714b8c4a17df78a2eac9]\nou_cd7f2733ddedc69e93a27e89cbf41c28: 高级全栈工程师需要哪些技能？"}],"timestamp":1776823826416}}
{"type":"message","id":"f4411198","parentId":"966f7928","timestamp":"2026-04-22T02:10:33.131Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户询问高级全栈工程师需要哪些技能，这是一个技术知识问答问题，我可以直接根据对全栈开发领域的理解来回答，不需要调用外部工具。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"高级全栈工程师是既能深入前端也能驾驭后端的\"多面手\"，需要更广泛的技术视野：\n\n## 🎨 前端深度\n\n**框架精通**\n- React/Vue/Angular 至少一门（通常两门）\n- TypeScript 重度使用\n- 状态管理：Redux/Zustand/Pinia\n- 构建工具：Vite/Webpack/Bun\n\n**工程化能力**\n- SSR/SSG：Next.js/Nuxt.js\n- 微前端架构\n- WebAssembly、PWA\n- 性能优化（Lighthouse 90+）\n- 测试：Jest/Cypress/Playwright\n\n**UI/UX 意识**\n- 响应式设计、移动端适配\n- CSS 框架（Tailwind/Styled-components）\n- 动画与交互细节\n- 可访问性（a11y）标准\n\n## ⚙️ 后端广度\n\n（同上：Go/Java/Node.js + 数据库 + 中间件 + 云原生）\n\n## 🚀 全栈特有技能\n\n**BFF 层 (Backend for Frontend)**\n- GraphQL / tRPC\n- Serverless 函数\n- API Gateway 设计\n\n**DevOps 一体化**\n- 从代码到部署全流程掌控\n- Docker Compose / K8s 基础\n- GitHub Actions / GitLab CI\n- 监控从前端到后端的完整链路\n\n**产品思维**\n- 能从 0 到 1 独立交付完整功能\n- 理解用户体验与技术实现的平衡\n- 快速原型验证（MVP）\n\n## 💡 软技能升级\n\n- **上下文切换能力**：能在 UI 细节和系统架构间灵活切换\n- **决策权衡**：知道何时用成熟方案 vs 创新技术\n- **沟通桥梁**：连接前后端团队，减少信息孤岛\n\n## 🏆 高阶要求\n\n- 设计并实施前端 Monorepo\n- 微前端架构落地经验\n- 跨平台：Electron/React Native\n- 技术选型：能说服团队采用新技术\n- 指导团队成员成长\n\n---\n\n**核心价值**：能独立负责一个产品从 UI 到 DB 的**整个技术闭环**，是小团队或创业公司的\"超级个体\"。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":19771,"output":559,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20330,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776823826417,"responseId":"chatcmpl-7b4e88cd-7c63-93e9-abe8-19176001e2fa"}}
