{"type":"message","id":"b98dccd3","parentId":"aba74939","timestamp":"2026-04-22T02:25:21.872Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户再次要求启动 Chrome，但我已经通过之前的 exec 命令确认 Chrome 已经在运行中了，需要告知用户 Chrome 已打开。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **Chrome 已经打开了！**\n\n从进程列表可以看到，Chrome 早就在运行了（从早上 9 点就开始跑），现在正开着多个标签页：\n\n- 🟢 Main process (PID 895) — 主进程\n- 📊 GPU Process — 图形加速\n- 🎨 Renderer Processes — 各个标签页的渲染进程\n- 🔧 Helper Services — 音频、网络、存储等服务\n\n**你想做什么？**\n- 🌐 访问某个网页？\n- 🔍 搜索什么内容？\n- 📄 读取某个页面的内容？\n- 📸 截图看看当前在浏览什么？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":38081,"output":203,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38284,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776824718860,"responseId":"chatcmpl-a1e8c6af-f207-9108-8e83-b8f97dd1d271"}}
