{"type":"message","id":"c7ab4afb","parentId":"6ff002a1","timestamp":"2026-04-22T03:28:32.276Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这个.gitignore 配置太简陋了，只忽略了两行内容，需要帮用户添加完整的敏感信息忽略规则包括 API Key、配置文件和环境变量。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在的 `.gitignore` 配置太简陋了！我来帮你完善一下：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_436602abd51b4ce98a21feb3","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/zhu/.openclaw/.gitignore","content":"# OpenClaw 敏感配置 - Git  ignore 规则\n\n## 🔑 API Keys & Secrets (核心安全)\n.env\n.env.local\n.env.*.local\n*.key\n*.pem\n*.secret\napi_key*\napikey*\nAPI_KEY*\nAUTH_TOKEN*\nACCESS_TOKEN*\nSECRET_KEY*\n\n## 📁 本地配置（不要上传）\nconfig/\nconfiguration.json\nsettings.local.json\nsecrets.yaml\ncredentials.json\n\n## 🗂️ Agent 运行时数据\nagents/*/models.json\nagents/*/logs/\nagents/*/cache/\nagents/*/temp/\n\n## 💾 数据库与存储\n*.db\n*.sqlite\n*.sqlite3\n*.mdb\ndata/\nstorage/\n\n## 🖼️ 临时文件\n*.tmp\n*.temp\n*.bak\n*.backup\n*.swp\n*.swo\n*~\n\n## 🌐 Node 相关\nnode_modules/\npackage-lock.json\nyarn.lock\npnpm-lock.yaml\n.pnpm-store/\n\n## 🎨 IDE 与编辑器\n.idea/\n.vscode/\n*.sublime-project\n*.sublime-workspace\n.DS_Store\nThumbs.db\n\n## 📊 构建产物\ndist/\nbuild/\nout/\n*.log\n\n## 🧪 测试临时文件\ncoverage/\n.nyc_output/\ntest-results/\n\n## 🤖 Docker\ndocker-compose.override.yml\n*.override.yml\n\n## 📝 其他项目特定忽略\n**.tgz\n**.tar.gz\n*.dmg\n\n## 🔒 OpenClaw 专用\nbrowser/user-data/\nplugins.cache\ngateway.token\n\n## ⚠️ 注意：可以公开的配置\n# *.json  # 如果你想保留 package.json 等公共配置\n# README.md  # 文档应该公开\n# LICENSE  # 许可证应该公开\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":42792,"output":524,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43316,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776828504727,"responseId":"chatcmpl-915c17d8-441b-9ab9-95fa-efc773547c76"}}
