{"type":"message","id":"ec263837","parentId":"413aa351","timestamp":"2026-04-22T03:31:10.332Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在 `.env` 文件已创建并设置好权限，需要向用户解释如何将配置文件中的硬编码 API Key 替换为环境变量引用。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 🎉 **完成！你现在有：**\n\n### ✅ **1. 安全存储的 `.env` 文件**\n\n位置：`/Users/zhu/.openclaw/.env`  \n权限：`600` (只有你自己可读)  \n状态：✅ 已被 Git 忽略\n\n---\n\n### 📝 **2. 如何使用环境变量？**\n\n#### **方式 A：在代码中读取（Node.js）**\n\n```javascript\n// package.json 中添加 dotenv\nimport 'dotenv/config';\n\n// 直接使用环境变量\nconst dashScopeKey = process.env.DASHSCOPE_API_KEY;\nconst feishuAppId = process.env.FEISHU_DEFAULT_APP_ID;\nconst feishuSecret = process.env.FEISHU_DEFAULT_APP_SECRET;\n```\n\n#### **方式 B：在 shell 脚本中**\n\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# 加载 .env\nsource /Users/zhu/.openclaw/.env\n\n# 使用变量\nexport OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_TOKEN=$OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_TOKEN\nexec openclaw gateway start\n```\n\n---\n\n### ⚙️ **3. 关于 OpenClaw 配置文件的说明**\n\nOpenClaw 的 `openclaw.json` 目前是 **静态配置**，不支持直接的环境变量引用（如 `${DASHSCOPE_API_KEY}`）。\n\n**但是！** 你可以通过以下方式实现：\n\n#### **方案一：运行时动态生成配置** ⭐ 推荐\n\n创建一个初始化脚本 `init.sh`：\n\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\ncd /Users/zhu/.openclaw\nsource .env\n\ncat > config.temp.json <<EOF\n{\n  \"models\": {\n    \"providers\": {\n      \"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com\": {\n        \"apiKey\": \"$DASHSCOPE_API_KEY\",\n        \"baseUrl\": \"https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/compatible-mode/v1\"\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"feishu\": {\n      \"accounts\": {\n        \"default\": {\n          \"appId\": \"$FEISHU_DEFAULT_APP_ID\",\n          \"appSecret\": \"$FEISHU_DEFAULT_APP_SECRET\"\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\nEOF\n\n# 然后备份原配置并替换\ncp openclaw.json openclaw.json.bak\nmv config.temp.json openclaw.json\n\n# 启动应用\nexec openclaw gateway start\n```\n\n#### **方案二：修改 OpenClaw 源码**（高级）\n\n如果你有 OpenClaw 源码，可以修改配置解析逻辑，支持环境变量占位符：\n\n```javascript\n// 伪代码示例\nfunction interpolateEnvVars(obj) {\n  return JSON.stringify(obj).replace(/\\$\\{(\\w+)\\}/g, (_, key) => {\n    return process.env[key] || '';\n  });\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 🔒 **4. 验证安全性**\n\n检查 `.env` 是否真的不会被提交：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c676977e25cc452382e94005","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/zhu/.openclaw && echo \"=== 测试 .gitignore ===\" && git status && echo -e \"\\n=== .env 是否会被跟踪？===\" && git ls-files --error-unmatch .env 2>&1 || echo \"✅ .env 不会被 Git 跟踪\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":50849,"output":803,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51652,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776828661166,"responseId":"chatcmpl-32349dfb-7da9-9b08-9182-c747c18db328"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8ee0c537","parentId":"ec263837","timestamp":"2026-04-22T03:31:10.384Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c676977e25cc452382e94005","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 测试 .gitignore ===\n位于分支 main\n\n尚无提交\n\n未跟踪的文件:\n  （使用 \"git add <文件>...\" 以包含要提交的内容）\n\t.gitignore\n\tagents/\n\tbrowser/\n\tcanvas/\n\tcompletions/\n\tcredentials/\n\tdevices/\n\texec-approvals.json\n\tfeishu/\n\tflows/\n\tidentity/\n\tlogs/\n\topenclaw.json\n\topenclaw.json.clobbered.2026-04-21T02-30-32-424Z\n\tsubagents/\n\ttasks/\n\tupdate-check.json\n\tworkspace/\n\n提交为空，但是存在尚未跟踪的文件（使用 \"git add\" 建立跟踪）\n\n=== .env 是否会被跟踪？===\n错误：路径规格 '.env' 未匹配任何 git 已知文件\nDid you forget to 'git add'?\n✅ .env 不会被 Git 跟踪"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":37,"aggregated":"=== 测试 .gitignore ===\n位于分支 main\n\n尚无提交\n\n未跟踪的文件:\n  （使用 \"git add <文件>...\" 以包含要提交的内容）\n\t.gitignore\n\tagents/\n\tbrowser/\n\tcanvas/\n\tcompletions/\n\tcredentials/\n\tdevices/\n\texec-approvals.json\n\tfeishu/\n\tflows/\n\tidentity/\n\tlogs/\n\topenclaw.json\n\topenclaw.json.clobbered.2026-04-21T02-30-32-424Z\n\tsubagents/\n\ttasks/\n\tupdate-check.json\n\tworkspace/\n\n提交为空，但是存在尚未跟踪的文件（使用 \"git add\" 建立跟踪）\n\n=== .env 是否会被跟踪？===\n错误：路径规格 '.env' 未匹配任何 git 已知文件\nDid you forget to 'git add'?\n✅ .env 不会被 Git 跟踪","cwd":"/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776828670383}}
{"type":"message","id":"f944f4be","parentId":"8ee0c537","timestamp":"2026-04-22T03:31:13.331Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"所有安全设置已完成并验证通过，现在需要给用户总结完成的工作内容和后续建议。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **确认！`.env` 文件绝对安全**，不会被提交到 Git！\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 **总结**\n\n| 项目 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| `.env` 文件创建 | ✅ 已创建 |\n| API Key 提取到环境变量 | ✅ 20+ 个密钥已转移 |\n| `.gitignore` 配置 | ✅ 已更新 |\n| 文件权限 | ✅ 仅自己可读 (600) |\n| Git 追踪检查 | ✅ 已通过验证 |\n\n---\n\n### 📌 **下一步建议：**\n\n1. **立即删除 `openclaw.json` 中的明文密钥**（可选）\n   ```bash\n   cp openclaw.json openclaw.json.bak.backup\n   # 然后手动编辑，替换为占位符\n   ```\n\n2. **创建启动脚本** `start.sh`：\n   - 自动加载 `.env`\n   - 生成临时配置文件\n   - 启动 OpenClaw\n\n3. **定期备份 `.env`**（离线存储，如加密压缩包）\n\n需要我帮你创建那个 `init.sh` 启动脚本吗？这样每次启动都会自动从环境变量读取配置！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":51843,"output":305,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52148,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776828670385,"responseId":"chatcmpl-c2239fc0-102d-9c0b-8960-f13a430ce64e"}}
